title: Glenn Gould - Consort of Musicke by Byrd and Gibbons
description:
CONSORT OF MUSICKE BY WILLIAM BYRD AND ORLANDO GIBBONS
Performed by Glenn Gould on piano

Includes "Fantasia in D" by Jan Sweelinck

SBM Super Bit Mapping by Sony in the early 1990s.

Track List

1 William Byrd - First Pavan and Galliard
2 Orlando Gibbons - Fantasy in C major
3 Orlando Gibbons - The Italian Ground (allemande)
4 William Byrd - Hughe Ashton's Ground
5 William Byrd - Sixth Pavan and Galliard
6 Orlando Gibbons - 'Lord of Salisbury' Pavan and Galliard
7 William Byrd - A Voluntary
8 William Byrd - Sellinger's Round
9 Jan Sweelinck - Fantasia in D (fantasia cromatica)
